This repository contains an header file which contains functions to interface 8051 microcontroller with a LCD display.

The LCD interfaced to the microcontroller is a 16*2 LCD display.

The pin details are as follows,

Pin 1 - Vss
Pin 2 - Vcc
Pin 3 - Vee
Pin 4 - RS
Pin 5 - R/W
Pin 6 - EN
Pin (7-14) - (D0-D7)

Optional-
Pin 15 - LED+
Pin 16 - LED-


The header file by default uses the PORT 2 as data line and Pins 3.0 3.1 3.2 for control signals RS, R/W, EN.
